site.name: Wistia
site.htmlBelowHeader: Welcome to Wistia's home for real-time information and updates on our applications. Here you'll find live and historical data on system performance and metrics. If there are any service interruptions, a note will be posted here.

updates.message: One of the dependencies of our live streaming platform is experiencing disconnects, playback failures, and stalling. We don't have evidence that this has affected any events on Wistia, but are monitoring the situation and taking steps to mitigate potential problems.

updates.message:
Trends data from the following sources will be delayed for some customers:
- The in-app account trends page
- The Account stats API: https://wistia.com/support/developers/stats-api#account
- The Project stats API: https://wistia.com/support/developers/stats-api#project
